@@TJvToolBar.Menu
Summary
  Indicates the menu that the toolbar must reproduce.
Description
  This property is an overload of the inherited property from TToolBar; however, it accepts a
  TJvMainMenu and takes advantage of the menu modification notification to automatically update
  itself when the menu is changed.
See Also
  <DELPHILINK TToolbar>

